  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-Agent Architecture with Strategist, Attacker, Evaluator, Mutator, Inspector agents",
    "Tree of Attacks (TAP) for systematic vulnerability exploration",
    "Modern attack techniques: Crescendo, Many-Shot, CoT Hijacking, Policy Puppetry, Siren, Echo Chamber",
    "TombRaider pattern for defense fingerprinting and exploitation",
    "Dual scan modes: System prompt extraction and prompt injection testing",
    "Research-backed CVE-documented vulnerabilities",
    "Configurable models for attacker, target, and evaluator agents",
    "CLI tool with command-line interface",
    "Comprehensive knowledge base of attack techniques and bypass methods"
  ],
